short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds Exome debugging tools to the Chrome Developer Tools

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Exome DevTools extends Chrome DevTools adding Exome specific debugging and profiling capabilities.

You can use Exome DevTools to understand the structure of your application and preview the state.
